keith-jordan.name: Keith Jordan
keith-jordan.bio: Founded the 1INGRESS Corporation in 2012. He was the co-founder of Fantainment Corporation, a not-for-profit corporation. Mr. Jordan has served in the U.S. Armed Service, U.S. Postal Service, and National Basketball Association as a recruiter/agent.

ronald-tasse.name: Ronald C Tassé
ronald-tasse.bio: Mr. Tassé’s work experience includes Teacher/Instructor Dickinson-Warren Business College (security hardware integration), Operations Manager, General Manager, and Sales Manager Electronics Department Rex Key & Security
